'''L3A1刺刀'''（{{Lang-en|L3A1 Bayonet}}）是[[英国|英国]][[英國軍隊|軍隊]]採用的套槍式多用途[[刺刀|刺刀]]，隨[[SA80槍族|L85步槍]]的採用同時起配用。（而衍生型L86和L22則無法安裝刺刀）
 
該刺刀基於[[FN_FAL自動步槍|FN FAL]] C型套槍式刺刀，但具有夾點式刀鋒。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://worldbayonets.com/Bayonet_Identification_Guide/fal_page/fal_bayonets.html |title=FAL Bayonets |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805154000/http://worldbayonets.com/Bayonet_Identification_Guide/fal_page/fal_bayonets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>它亦具有空心式握柄，可套在[[SA80槍族|SA80／L85步槍]]的[[槍口|槍口]]，並藉由插槽裝定使得握柄上的開口與[[消焰器|消焰器]]以上的孔洞對齊。刀身偏向握柄側面，以使槍彈從刀身側邊通過。它亦可以用作多功能刀，以及與刀鞘結合作為鐵絲剪鉗。刀鞘以上還具有磨刀石和折疊式鋸片。<ref name="sadefensejournal.com">{{cite journal|url=http://sadefensejournal.com/wp/?p=531|work=Small Arms Defense Journal|title=Are We Forever Stuck with the Bayonet?|first=George|last=Kontis|journal=|access-date=2020-10-10|archive-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905180148/http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/?p=531|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
== 概述 ==
L3A1的刀身偏向握柄右側，以在安裝刺刀時，步槍仍可發射子彈；它的形狀可在刺入時產生良好的貫穿力，並能將人的肋骨分斷而不埋入骨頭當中，還有其凹入部分的血道使得鮮血從身體徹底流出，以及肋條狀的排齒可用於切繩。刺刀握柄的形狀使得其本身可在需要時用作{{Link-en|格鬥刀|Fighting knife}}與多功能刀。與刺刀發配的刀鞘具有用於砍削木材的鋸片，打磨刺刀的[[磨刀石|磨刀石]]和[[开瓶器|开瓶器]]等獨立功能。當藉由凸起駐筍與刺刀結合時，它也可以用作鐵絲剪鉗。<ref name="sadefensejournal.com"/><ref name=AC71374>{{cite book|author=[[英國國防部|英國國防部]] |title = Army Code No. 71374, Infantry Training Volume II, Pamphlet No. 6 The SA 80 Rifle and Light Support Weapon (LSW) (All Arms)|work= |year= 1988}}</ref><ref name=AC718072004>{{cite book|author=[[英國國防部|英國國防部]] |title = Army Code No. 71807, Infantry Training Volume II, Pamphlet No. 5 The SA80 A2 (5.56 mm) System (Rifle, Light Support Weapon and Carbine) and Associated Equipment|work= |year= 2004}}</ref><ref name=AC718072011>{{cite book|author=[[英國國防部|英國國防部]] |title = Army Code No. 71807, Infantry Training Volume II, Pamphlet No. 5 The SA80 A2 (5.56 mm) System (Rifle, Light Support Weapon and Carbine) and Associated Equipment|work= |year= 2011}}</ref><ref name=AC718072015>{{cite book|author=[[英國國防部|英國國防部]] |title = Army Code No. 71807, Infantry Training Volume II, Pamphlet No. 5 The SA80 A2 (5.56 mm) System (Rifle, Light Support Weapon and Carbine) and Associated Equipment|work= |year= 2015}}</ref><ref name=WPN49>{{cite book |last1=Grant |first1=Neil |title=SA80 Assault Rifles |date=2016 |publisher=[[魚鷹出版|魚鷹出版]] |isbn=978-1-4728-1104-2}}</ref>

2004年5月14日，在{{Link-en|阿瑪拉戰役|Battle of Danny Boy}}當中，{{Link-en|威爾斯親王皇家團|Princess of Wales's Royal Regiment}}所屬的士兵以他倆上刺刀的SA80作戰；這是自[[马岛战争|福克蘭群島戰爭]]以來，英國軍隊首次使用上刺刀的步槍。<ref>{{cite news|last=Wyatt|first=Caroline|title=Remembering the Battle of Al Amara|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8016685.stm|work=BBC News|accessdate=9 April 2011|date=28 April 2009|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207040133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8016685.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在阿富汗的衝突當中，也有多次使用上刺刀的步槍的例子。<ref name=WPN49/>
[[File:British_Army_Royal_Military_Academy_Sandhurst,_Exercise_Dynamic_Victory_151110-A-HE359-023.jpg|thumb]]
該刺刀無法安裝在L22卡賓槍<ref name=AC70166>{{cite book|author=[[英國國防部|英國國防部]] |title = Army Code No. 70166 (Revised 1990) [Amended 2009], The Drill Manual|work= |year= 2009}}</ref>或是L86輕型支援武器以上；做成的結果是在{{Link-en|格蘭比行動|Operation Granby}}之中、清掃塹壕期間，裝備後者的士兵有時會與載具駕駛員的L85交換武器。<ref name=WPN49/>

英軍採用了[[L129A1精確射手步槍|L129A1精確射手步槍]]以後，亦採用了[[ISTEC技術服務有限公司|ISTEC公司]]所研發、藉由[[皮卡汀尼導軌|皮卡汀尼導軌]]裝上的適配器，使得L3A1刺刀可裝在L129A1以上使用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.istec.co.uk/index.php/products/ancillaries/bayonet-adaptor|title=Bayonet Adaptor|author=ISTEC Services|access-date=2020-04-07|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407181857/https://www.istec.co.uk/index.php/products/ancillaries/bayonet-adaptor|dead-url=no}}</ref>

